<br>
Whats the best way, in your opinion, to complete this part? Should I just get an enchanter to charm the quest NPCs? Bandit Sashes? Just lookin for some insight.<br>
<br>
Thanks in advance.<br>
<br>
-milo<br>
<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uellendilhsilvermist.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Ellendilh Silvermist</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://home.earthlink.net/~phiphix/ellendihlchibby.gif width=33 height=37 BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(3/21/01 7:47:26 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Surefall Glade &amp; Epic Quest Faction</span><hr size=1> Surefall is not aligned to Millers' faction (KaranaResidents). I know it for sure, as I also happily slaughered the Millers in my youth and I did the rose quest without any problem. Afterall, there is an NPC inside Surefall who tells you about how bad they are for being poachers. To me, that was a hint that I needed to kill them ;-)<br>
<br>
If you are KOS there, it is for another reason. <p><b><a href="http://eq.castersrealm.com/players/view_profile.asp?Id=19224">Ellendilh Silvermist</a></b><br>
<a href="http://www.secretguardians.com">Secret Guardians</a><br>
<FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2>Wandering Hierophant from Prexus.</font><br>
<i><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>~~~~~ Wuoshi Certified Bus Line ~~~~~</font></i></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/umilosch.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Milosch</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(3/21/01 8:00:06 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Surefall Glade &amp; Epic Quest Faction</span><hr size=1> Hrmmm, gonna have to find out what faction they are on then. I wonder if qeynos guards have something to do with it...<br>
<br>
-milo <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/utrishthistlecone.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Trish Thistlecone</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(3/21/01 9:18:28 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> surefall glade</span><hr size=1> I am a level 44 1/2 elf druid and definitely kos in surefall.  My best guess is it's because I got so much pleasure out of killing Holly in QH for all the times she killed my other characters.  Not sure how to increase faction here to make up for it. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uzeniabigbootea.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Zenia Bigbootea</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(3/21/01 4:53:22 pm)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://www.hippieguild.com/images/small.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: surefall glade</span><hr size=1> killin qeynos guards will down your treehugger faction<br>
<br>
Jaggedpine Treefolk or somthing like that, but killing gnolls in BB will raise it, and they are VERY green just run a dozen or so around and quake it<br>
<br>
Zen <p>Zenia 57 Druid
Craxx 51 Warrior</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/umilosch.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Milosch</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(3/21/01 5:03:30 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: surefall glade</span><hr size=1> Gonna go give it a whirl Zenia. Thanks for the info :)<br>
<br>
-milo <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/urolemeggido.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Role Meggido</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(3/22/01 4:19:25 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> gnolls</span><hr size=1> If you are killing gnolls save their teeth.  You can turn them in for good faction bumps in Halas or S Queynos.<br>
<br>
Also there is a named gnoll called gnasher furgot that spawns in the hills around midnight.  If you kill him you can loot his head and turn it in in surefall for good faction.<br>
<br>
If you get high enough faction though you can go into surefall and kill bandits for bumps. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/umilosch.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Milosch</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(3/22/01 5:39:41 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: gnolls</span><hr size=1> Thanks Role. Real good info, which I'll put to use in the future I'm sure. Just need to be non-KOS atm tho (i think) for the rose of firona portion of my epic :)<br>
<br>
Thanks for all the info<br>
<br>
-Milo<br>
